5. Summary of Historical Exploration at Glen Isla 	5
EPM 16314 was lodged 05/04/2007 by John Kingsley, and was granted for
Year three exploration included field exploration, sampling and metal
detecting. The Rock chip sample locations were overlayed on the EPM map to help
re-interpret some of the mapping. Past geological mapping was accessed and Mapinfo
used to produce a Geological map of EPM 16314(See Appendices 4 and 5). Twenty
four rock chip samples were assayed and the results included in Appendix 3.
